  "sections": {
    "gp_section_572012432579363992": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "342645e5f95b7e49eac1c5e80600fa4396de67509d742872f58ef5b5e8cf152a_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>Keep the bottle in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Do not refrigerate. Always store out of reach of children.</p>",
        "gg5QWW06sGv_text": "<p>SciatiCalm is designed for adults. If you are pregnant, nursing, or under 18, consult a healthcare provider before use. It is generally safe for seniors when taken as directed.</p>",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>While SciatiCalm contains natural, well-tolerated ingredients, we always recommend consulting your doctor if you are currently taking prescription medications or have a medical condition.</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>No, SciatiCalm is only available online through our official website. This allows us to keep prices low and ensure product authenticity.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Each serving contains:</p><ul><li>Organic Turmeric Root Powder – 900mg</li><li>Turmeric Root Extract (95% Standardized Curcuminoids) – 100mg</li><li>BioPerine® (Black Pepper Fruit Extract) – 7mg</li><li>All ingredients are encapsulated in a gelatin capsule.</li></ul>",
        "ggRWVQP7xyG_text": "<p>Each bottle contains 90 capsules — enough for 30 days when taken as directed.</p>",
        "ggT40bKuK75_text": "<p>Take 3 capsules per day, ideally with food. Most users take all 3 in the morning or split the dose between breakfast and dinner.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>Some users begin to notice reduced discomfort within 5–7 days. Most report significant improvement within 2–4 weeks, with continued benefits over 45–90 days of consistent use.</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>Can I buy SmoothSpine™ SciatiCalm in stores?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>What ingredients are in SmoothSpine™ SciatiCalm?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_10": "<p>What is your return policy?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>Is SciatiCalm safe to take with my current medications?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>How should I store SciatiCalm?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>Will the SciatiCalm supplement help with my nerve pain?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p>How long until I feel relief from my nerve pain?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_6": "<p>How often should I take the supplement?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_7": "<p>How many capsules are in each bottle?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_8": "<p>Are there any age or health restrictions?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_9": "<p>What if the supplement doesn’t work for me?</p>",
        "gghn7pMgHJ7_text": "<p>We stand behind SciatiCalm with a 90-day money-back guarantee. If you’re not satisfied for any reason, simply contact us and we’ll refund your order — no hassle, no questions asked.</p>",
        "ggrcqOh_tmz_text": "<p>SciatiCalm is formulated to support nerve health, reduce inflammation, and promote myelin repair — all of which are important in managing sciatica and nerve-related discomfort. Many users report a noticeable reduction in pain, tingling, and burning sensations within weeks.</p>",
        "ggzmHVH4LpH_text": "<p>Every order is backed by our 90-day risk-free guarantee. If you’re not happy with your results, return the product (even empty bottles) within 90 days for a full refund.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572012432579363992"
    },
    "gp_section_572012432579429528": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "4bd77d6e0acd07b964e99ab5071c36711808a882479c928dcc42317c9f379f7d_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-6uMF1_Nj_text": "<p>It’s natural support that fits into your life. Not the other way around.</p>",
        "gg0znNmAU8T_text": "<p><strong>More comfortable movement during the day</strong></p>",
        "gg3GwCpV-GT_text": "<p><strong>Less nerve pressure and burning</strong></p>",
        "gg5A_s7vPft_text": "<p>With daily use, people notice:</p>",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Built On Science. Trusted By Experts.",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "SciatiCalm Helped Over 57,000+ Customers Naturally Relieve Nerve Pain",
        "ggB_uZ99e5h_text": "<p>These aren’t trendy buzzwords. They’re <strong>science-based facts</strong> supported by peer-reviewed research and the insights of doctors, neuropathy specialists, and functional medicine professionals.</p>",
        "ggBo6yCs99D_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-47327e19-300c-4816-8fdb-db6ead19acde.webp",
        "ggFsSgIrq63_text": "<p><strong>Synergistic formula amplifies effectiveness:</strong></p><p>Combining curcumin with piperine (black pepper extract) has been shown to work more powerfully — enhancing curcumin’s anti-pain effects by up to 76% in preclinical models<strong><sup>3</sup></strong>.</p>",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "SciatiCalm Helped Over 57,000+ Customers Naturally Relieve Nerve Pain",
        "ggOLny2Lf9H_text": "<p><strong>Fewer flare-ups when sitting, walking, or sleeping</strong></p>",
        "ggOtS3jO5zX_text": "<p><strong>Enhanced absorption for real results:</strong></p><p>BioPerine® dramatically increases curcumin’s bioavailability — making it 20 times more available in the body compared to when curcumin is taken alone<strong><sup>4</sup></strong>.</p>",
        "ggSvIZrM2QP_text": "<p><strong>A better sense of energy and calm in the body</strong></p>",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p><strong>Clinically shown to support nerve repair:</strong></p><p>Curcumin has been found to help restore the protective myelin sheath around nerves and counteract peripheral neuropathy, reducing pain and improving function in clinical models<strong><sup>1</sup></strong>.</p>",
        "ggUHGJ1A2mE_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-636c78dd-688d-41e5-b3cd-987459f0114f.png",
        "ggYhZQDCRPW_text": "<p>No more guesswork. No more taking painkillers that just mask symptoms. Just two capsules a day of clean, high-potency ingredients your body actually recognizes — and uses.</p>",
        "ggcllM8jPEK_text": "<p><strong>SciatiCalm </strong>doesn’t just say it works — it’s designed to work, with proven ingredients in proven doses trusted by experts.</p>",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>When you choose SciatiCalm, you’re relying on more than clever marketing — you’re aligning with real science and expert endorsements:</p>",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p><strong>SciatiCalm has quietly become one of the most trusted daily supplements for people dealing with sciatic nerve pain, inflammation, and chronic discomfort.</strong></p>",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Built On Science. Trusted By Experts.",
        "gglp0HJCFVA_text": "<p><strong>Proven anti-inflammatory action:</strong></p><p>Curcumin reduces inflammation by suppressing glial cell activation — helping calm spinal neuroinflammation, a key driver of chronic nerve pain<strong><sup>2</sup></strong>.</p>",
        "ggo2I27ACrO_text": "<p>And because it’s made with enhanced turmeric extract, black pepper for absorption, and real, research-backed dosing, <strong>SciatiCalm actually helps your body fight inflammation at the source.</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572012432579429528"
    },
    "gp_section_572012432579495064": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9da0bda984dd5b5ace699543ae26cb07e70cf52e7bbd078b02e7a24feedff4e3_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg2skFYSnGC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-51bd7b08-f4ec-461e-bc36-e7734dd26e06.jpg",
        "ggBZyLN-waC_text": "<p>Your order today is protected by our iron-clad 90-day <strong>100% money-back guarantee. </strong>If you don't experience the remarkable <strong>relief from sciatica and nerve pain</strong> that you were anticipating, or if you're not amazed by how much easier it is to move, then at any time in the next <strong>90 days,</strong> let us know and we will refund every single penny of your investment. <strong>No questions asked.</strong></p>",
