    "gp_section_572012432579626136": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "23b71138587de2d093df1a3cc51be201effd1b94a0fd10eac1400275074a82c3_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1WJODqwGE_text": "<p>Costs Hundreds of Dollars a Month</p>",
        "gg1l9ZsD4ZL_text": "Other Pain Relief Methods",
        "gg35L5tHWLl_text": "<p>Most drugs and treatments offer short-term relief without fixing the underlying inflammation damaging your sciatic nerve or myelin sheath.</p>",
        "gg6YHdZykSx_text": "SmoothSpine SciatiCalm",
        "gg8B9W6Nh6g_text": "<p>Traditional meds can negatively impact your stomach, liver, and mood — trading one problem for another.</p>",
        "ggAE6F26brb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggFlaRsfX_r_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggGTEluwLZX_text": "<p>Clinically Studied Natural Ingredients</p>",
        "ggOZidTxPrt_text": "<p>Costs Less Than a Coffee a Day</p>",
        "ggS6aIr0DXf_text": "<p>Can Disrupt Other Areas of Health</p>",
        "ggU6Cofrkcy_text": "<p>Risk of Unpleasant Side Effects</p>",
        "ggZWYjcI0Sj_text": "<p>It’s non-addictive, works fast, and actually does GOOD things for your body.</p>",
        "gg_uUJJZYot_text": "<p>Targets the Root Cause, Not Just the Pain</p>",
        "ggabMzZulc1_text": "<p>Only Masks Symptoms Temporarily</p>",
        "ggcFzCiQ6WE_text": "<p>Curcumin isn’t just good for your nerves — it also supports joints, digestion, and immune health, making it a smart long-term wellness choice.</p>",
        "ggcIYxRgigt_text": "<p>Improves Overall Inflammation and Joint Health</p>",
        "ggchiUpfJH2_text": "SmoothSpine SciatiCalm Is the Safer, Healthier, More Effective Choice",
        "ggd0hjAxMgS_text": "<p>Backed by research, our turmeric-curcumin blend is bio-enhanced for maximum absorption and effect — with no synthetic fillers, no addictive compounds, and no crash.</p>",
        "gggZo7nOlQf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggiY6BubJDN_text": "<p>Many prescription meds come with nausea, dizziness, drowsiness, or dependency — and still don’t resolve the actual nerve pain over time.</p>",
        "ggnUORZ6q9u_text": "<p>Unlike painkillers that just mask the symptoms, SciatiCalm helps calm nerve inflammation and supports healthy nerve repair — so relief keeps improving over time, not wearing off.</p>",
        "ggopNT52XXD_text": "<p>At under $1.50 per serving, SciatiCalm is affordable, especially compared to costly therapies, injections, or visits that can run hundreds per month.</p>",
        "ggplNJpBZcA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-23ff5eac-98d6-4932-bb00-6836a417b18e.png",
        "ggqa-TsithJ_text": "<p>PT sessions, prescriptions, and repeated doctor visits can stack up fast. One user told us their nerve injection bill hit &nbsp;$320 in a single month — with no lasting results.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572012432579626136"
    },
