    "gp_section_572012432579757208": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9d777d2d4d957254c2f46d4c56f317364b64d0843ac9d46d6502191d09491c4f_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-RifOCijk_text": "<p>Each capsule combines <strong>bio-enhanced turmeric</strong> (curcumin extract) with <strong>black pepper fruit extract</strong> for maximum absorption. Together, they help reduce swelling around the sciatic nerve, relieve pressure, and support the regeneration of the <strong>myelin sheath</strong> — the barrier your body needs to protect itself from those sharp, shooting pains.</p>",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>That’s exactly why we created <strong>SciatiCalm </strong>— a supplement designed to do what stretches and painkillers can’t: <strong>calm nerve inflammation at the source</strong> and support your body’s ability to heal the protective layer around your nerves.</p>",
        "ggQsjbwtdZb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-2aeefdce-44d6-4a49-b001-0f939f5430a3.png",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "The Real Relief Starts When the Inflammation Stops",
        "ggkgBw2113r_text": "<p>No temporary numbing. No guesswork. Just real, clinical-strength support to help you sit, sleep, and move again without fear of flare-ups.</p>",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "The Real Relief Starts When the Inflammation Stops"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572012432579757208"
    },
    "gp_section_572012432579822744": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "28b373c5f4e539373aa0da4f3f745344c345f69d90fa9698a7bac663aa2ee913_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0045cZav__text": "<p>Your nervous system becomes inflamed. The myelin sheath — the protective layer around your nerves — starts to degrade. And that exposes your nerves to pain, compression, and misfiring signals.</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>But your nerve pain keeps coming back — the real reason may surprise you.</p>",
        "gg6488J9La7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-c179b183-a57b-4b75-9526-633781e94b8c.webp",
        "gg8MDjGBaur_text": "<p>That’s why even light pressure or gentle movement can feel like electric shocks or stabbing pain.</p>",
        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>I Thought I’d Be Living With Sciatica Forever… But Then I Started Taking SmoothSpine SciatiCalm</strong></span>",
        "ggQAm8x-ujQ_text": "<p>Most chronic nerve pain and inflammation are caused by something called:</p>",
        "ggRTR9XYKM9_text": "<p><strong>“Inflammatory Nerve Breakdown”</strong></p>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "Why Your Nerve Pain Won’t Go Away(Until This Is Fixed)",
        "ggWaLe4w3DQ_text": "<p>Over time, when your body is exposed to stress, overuse, injury, or even poor sleep...</p>",
        "ggic0fflxUn_text": "<p>Until you cool the inflammation and <strong>support the repair of the myelin sheath</strong> — you’re just covering up the symptoms. Not healing.</p>",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>If you’ve tried ice packs, heating pads, stretches, painkillers, or even surgery...</p>",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "Why Your Nerve Pain Won’t Go Away (Until This Is Fixed)"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-572012432579822744"
    },
